  "key": "G major",
  "genre": [
    "Ballad",
    "Ambient"
  ],
  "difficultyLevel": 3,
  "lyrics": "Yeah, it's beauty, it's beauty Why we go through this life just going up two degrees? Why we here for the pain, why we here for the torture, baby? Yeah, it's beauty, it's beauty You and me, whichever way the wind blows, the time goes You know, you know that it's beauty, it's beauty It's beauty, you and me Beauty through the strings of what that could be And what we see in front of us As the time lapse in, I'm just seeing you Or is it me in a different point of view? I know that my heart is here Your heart, I can think I can see it through the fog of the glass It's beauty, beauty You and me in this century of haste Can we find balance of the greed in our own self? It's beauty, it's beauty Beauty right in front of me I think there's all this beauty, beauty You and me, all in front of me tonight Which way is right? Take everything you wanna take, everything you had Throw it in the dumpster, throw it out back for the new Something beautiful about that view Yeah, the beauty, the beauty You and me in eternity How many times did you climb that ladder to get here next to me? It's beauty, it's beauty",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 19.799999237060547,
      "text": "Yeah, it's beauty, it's beauty Why we go through this life just going up",
      "start": 12.300000190734863
    },
    {
      "end": 20.920000076293945,
      "text": "two degrees?",
      "start": 19.799999237060547
    },
    {
      "end": 26.399999618530273,
      "text": "Why we here for the pain, why we here for the torture, baby?",
      "start": 21.959999084472656
    },
    {
      "end": 29.979999542236328,
      "text": "Yeah, it's beauty, it's beauty",
      "start": 26.6200008392334
    },
    {
      "end": 36.880001068115234,
      "text": "You and me, whichever way the wind blows, the time goes",
      "start": 30.6200008392334
    },
    {
      "end": 43.97999954223633,
      "text": "You know, you know that it's beauty, it's beauty",
      "start": 36.880001068115234
    },
    {
      "end": 57.97999954223633,
      "text": "It's beauty, you and me",
      "start": 52.84000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 63.84000015258789,
      "text": "Beauty through the strings of what that could be",
      "start": 58.619998931884766
    },
    {
      "end": 68.12000274658203,
      "text": "And what we see in front of us",
      "start": 64.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 71.4000015258789,
      "text": "As the time lapse in, I'm just seeing you",
      "start": 68.12000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 74.36000061035156,
      "text": "Or is it me in a different point of view?",
      "start": 71.4000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 76.37999725341797,
      "text": "I know that my heart is here",
